<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个星期后，老先生从火车窗口看到了新的东西，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是另一张写着字的白布：妈妈好多了，谢谢！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们决定告诉妈妈他们做的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈非常生气，然后突然哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哭是会传染的，很快，大家都哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈先停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她擦干眼泪说：“对不起，我不该生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我知道你们想帮忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们是很穷，这是事实，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但你们不应该告诉别人，也不应该向陌生人要东西！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不是故意的。”鲍比哭着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起！”菲利斯和彼得也哭着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会给老先生写感谢信的。”妈妈抱着他们说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们可以让站长帮忙把信转交给他，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这件事我们都忘了吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们走出房间以后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比说：“妈妈真好，其他大人生气后都不会道歉的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。”彼得说，“但是她生气的时候很可怕。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把信送到了火车站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天正好是鲍比的生日。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天下午，孩子们叫鲍比先去外面，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下午茶的时候再回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不能偷看，我们会给你一个惊喜。”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比去了花园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她回来的时候，菲利斯和彼得在后门等她，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后带她去前门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们跟平时不一样，收拾得很干净，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯的头上还系着一个红色的蝴蝶结。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们和妈妈一起站在桌子旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>桌子上有12支蜡烛，因为鲍比12岁了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>桌子上有面包、果酱和一个大蛋糕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>桌子上还有从花园里采的花，以及几个小礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“生日快乐，鲍比！”他们开心地大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快打开礼物吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>礼物都很棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯送了一条精致的手帕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈送了一枚她自己的玫瑰胸针。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比想要妈妈这枚胸针很久。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>维尼夫人送了一个花瓶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我送你的礼物。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把火车头玩具放在桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面装满了糖果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得要把自己最珍贵的火车头送给她？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是火车头。”彼得赶紧说，“只是糖果。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是彼得看了看鲍比的表情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是说，不是整个火车头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你愿意的话，可……可以送你一半。”他鼓起勇气说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，彼得！”鲍比说，“这个礼物很棒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比心想：“彼得愿意给我一半的火车头，他真好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗯……那我要坏掉的那一半，然后修好它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在看看蛋糕吧。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比仔细看了看蛋糕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蛋糕上有个用花做的图案。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是铁路的地图！”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>喝完茶，妈妈和他们一起玩游戏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是一个美好的生日。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，鲍比轻轻地下楼去拿礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比看到妈妈坐在桌子旁边，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手里拿着一支笔和一些信纸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈要给爸爸写信。”鲍比想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，妈妈一直没有开始写。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈头枕着胳膊，趴在了桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天是我的生日，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈肯定不想让我知道她不开心。”鲍比想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她悄悄地回到自己的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美好的生日派对，却是一个伤心的结尾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>